This tool is used to control the ardrone_moves node "position_control".
It provides a GUI to set target, start/stop position control,
but also provides tools for manual drone control
These commands can have a displayed button and a keyboard shortcut
(specified in ())
takeoff (k)
land (l)
emergency stop (ESC)
toggle cam (,) -> switch between front and bottom cameras

fly command are optimized for azerty keyboard)
forward (Z)
back (S)
left (Q)
rigth (D)
up (P)
down (M)
rotate left (A)
rotate right (E)

